      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"never truly there to begin with\"... that's a heavy thing to say. It makes it feel like there was no point in trying to keep hold of anything. Like fighting the erasure is just a waste of energy. Do you really think it's better? Just to stop fighting and let it happen?",
